{"tid":2430374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國安法掀知名學者出走潮　港大微生物學系地震","createTime":"2021-03-03T01:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T04:59:08.000Z","uid":271829,"like":296,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"274c138b92e3cd8a6447001648b605965ae12492","tid":2430374,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PEl99KRwtUR5BY5G05knPW7ITxY=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S64OKPUS6FFLJKTD5IXZUIBAZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPEl99KRwtUR5BY5G05knPW7ITxY%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS64OKPUS6FFLJKTD5IXZUIBAZE.jpg&h=c8eeed20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港大微生物學系前系主任胡釗逸（左圖）及劉嘉珮（右圖）夫婦，在國安法生效同月請辭。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n肝病權威黎青龍不獲續約，本港醫學界隨時再失去極具份量的重要一員。事實上，去年國安法生效後，已先後有多位知名學者出走，公共醫療醫生協會會長馬仲儀相信，在學術自由「低氣壓」之下，不但海外醫學專家不願意來港教授，即使選擇留下來繼續研究的學者，未來也許變得更低調，不肯受訪或觸及任何敏感議題。<br />\n<br />\n港大微生物學系地震<br />\n去年7月國安法生效後，最先離開的知名學者是港大微生物學系兩名前系主任胡釗逸及劉嘉珮夫婦，他們7月請辭、10月離任，據報二人在香港以外繼續研究。二人請辭可謂該系近年最大的人事變動，據悉系方亦始料不及，簡單進行全球招募及系內遴選後，最終擢升40歲出頭的臨床副教授杜啟泓接任系主任一職。而政府抗疫專家組成員、港大公共衞生學院院長福田敬二去年10月不獲港大續約，今年底完成五年合約後將離開。<br />\n中文大學前校長、腸胃科專家沈祖堯亦在國安法生效後一個月表明將會離開香港，到新加坡南洋理工大學擔任醫學院院長和高級副校長。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210303/CLX2MC5QORGZDAGIJ5KDVOCCF4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210303%2FCLX2MC5QORGZDAGIJ5KDVOCCF4%2F&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiuhR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=42a4bd72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210303%2FCLX2MC5QORGZDAGIJ5KDVOCCF4%2F&h=83ac7534\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210303/CLX2MC5QORGZDAGIJ5KDVOCCF4/</a>"},{"pid":"e88d03e3a3b94e9cc688c935edc7574484cf860c","tid":2430374,"uid":79563,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:46:27.000Z","msg":"走<br />\n<br />\n仲留係度無意思"},{"pid":"3019b39a750df386a218ccaf80c71bd30c7d1a67","tid":2430374,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ea12d0fa17785e1deb5dddff9d7a818d82e926","tid":2430374,"uid":292987,"like":110,"dislike":0,"score":110,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:51:52.000Z","msg":"XGDX就嚟變普通話教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74da52d52ef02b4fb08274b9089c728907778843","tid":2430374,"uid":6192,"like":124,"dislike":1,"score":123,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:52:44.000Z","msg":"走得好<br />\n香港唔值得有人材"},{"pid":"5794f11c3b8de560dbc0fb4714d0ae11f44083d9","tid":2430374,"uid":353256,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:53:32.000Z","msg":"唔知袁國勇幾時比人炒呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d880bc25cce8e949fad1b0bcc51ed363cec1eb6","tid":2430374,"uid":254450,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:54:16.000Z","msg":"唔該再走多d，最好班有料嘅專業人士走撚晒佢，淨返果班就去拎綜援，食死港共為止"},{"pid":"da3b8a292d2fc95b619e4cca8a0a2b33440d4fb4","tid":2430374,"uid":30040,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5794f11c3b8de560dbc0fb4714d0ae11f44083d9","tid":2430374,"uid":353256,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:53:32.000Z","msg":"唔知袁國勇幾時比人炒呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:55:23.000Z","msg":"佢好似話佢下年退休？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5207427125f794b7fe3ffcf6231dc4be4a3403f9","tid":2430374,"uid":223428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:55:24.